      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "SCRUB'S BLUE (1) has missed the frame the last couple but was a OPEN winner three back (25.40) at this track over 457m. Looks suited here and big improvement expected. FLAGMAN FRANKY (2) shapes well for this after winning last start over the 390m at this track in a powerful 21.69. Harder here but will be in this for a long way. SIRONEN TIGER (7) was strongly fancied latest and proved too good with a 3.5 lengths win at this track in a handy 25.13. Wide box to overcome but goes well over this trip. Has a very good strike-rate from this draw, with three wins from three starts. Expected to feature again. STAR FERNANDO (6) cannot be ruled out.",
